616
00:37:26,700 --> 00:37:28,430
so that Father can feel at ease.

617
00:37:29,530 --> 00:37:32,010
Take care of them,

618
00:37:32,950 --> 00:37:34,610
in case anything goes wrong.

619
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:36,980
I will follow your advice.

620
00:37:45,690 --> 00:37:47,070
Since Father is fine,

621
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:50,680
I and Xiyuan will leave first.

622
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:02,900
Let's continue.

623
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:03,700
Come on.

624
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:04,520
