you and Princess Shangguan

631
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:20,020
would have good news this time.

632
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:20,500
Mother.

633
00:38:20,860 --> 00:38:23,550
It's not convenient for us in the outside world.

634
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:25,880
Besides, us coming back

635
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:26,870
is also good news.

636
00:38:26,870 --> 00:38:27,400
Isn't it?

637
00:38:27,830 --> 00:38:28,670
It is.

638
00:38:29,230 --> 00:38:31,650
But we're all looking forward to our grandchildren.

639
00:38:31,650 --> 00:38:32,390
Hurry up.

640
00:38:33,470 --> 00:38:34,030
Yes.

641
00:38:34,050 --> 00:38:35,050
The main thing is,

642
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:37,090
Qi, you have to overcome the problems.

643
00:38:37,090 --> 00:38:37,750
You too, An.

644
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:38,610
Okay.

645
00:38:39,980 --> 00:38:41,310
You should all hurry up.

646
00:38:42,390 --> 00:38:44,180
