656
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,350
I can nurse my body.

657
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,960
It can always get better.

658
00:39:20,470 --> 00:39:21,440
This child

659
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:24,120
is going to be born in our family.

660
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:27,610
