661
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:31,480
He has the responsibility to fight for the future with us.

662
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:32,380
No way.

663
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,490
It's too dangerous.

664
00:39:35,020 --> 00:39:36,690
