666
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:42,400
Even the Lord's scruples are nothing now.

667
00:39:43,830 --> 00:39:46,650
As long as this child is the eldest grandson,

668
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:48,920
he'll have exceptional status.

669
00:39:49,690 --> 00:39:51,380
That's the most important thing.

670
00:39:51,380 --> 00:39:52,510
