672
00:39:54,010 --> 00:39:55,870
There's no “what if”. It has to be.

673
00:40:00,850 --> 00:40:02,090
If he's not a boy,

674
00:40:08,930 --> 00:40:10,620
I'll make him a boy.

675
00:40:29,690 --> 00:40:30,720
Don't feel reserved.

676
00:40:30,720 --> 00:40:31,380
Just say it.

677
00:40:31,750 --> 00:40:32,190
Yes.

678
00:40:33,200 --> 00:40:34,930
My Lord, you're mostly healed.

679
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:38,480
You just need to recuperate in the next six months

680
00:40:38,770 --> 00:40:40,230
and don't exert yourself.

681
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,940
I'm just getting a bit weak

682
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:46,460
after the illness.

683
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:49,460
But I'm not that weak.

684
00:40:50,490 --> 00:40:53,830
