685
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,120
Father, you've just recovered from your illness.

686
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:59,470
It's better to follow the doctor's advice.

687
00:40:59,470 --> 00:41:00,270
But Doctor Xu,

688
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,560
