689
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:03,810
can you give him a day's grace

690
00:41:03,810 --> 00:41:04,560
before resuming the diet?

691
00:41:04,560 --> 00:41:04,980
Yes.

692
00:41:06,540 --> 00:41:09,100
Please remember not to drink alcohol.

693
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:13,480
Doctor Xu.

694
00:41:13,820 --> 00:41:16,790
Now that I'm free from the diet, I'm not allowed to drink.

695
00:41:16,790 --> 00:41:19,150
You have to restrict me on one thing.

696
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:21,780
Reporting!

697
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:24,890
I'll leave now.

698
00:41:25,640 --> 00:41:26,150
My Lord.

699
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:28,190
Prince Jun's lady has given birth to a baby boy.

700
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:29,250
Congratulations.

701
00:41:30,940 --> 00:41:32,540
It's said it was almost time.

702
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:35,260
I didn't expect it to be today.

703
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,060
Congratulations to the Lord.

704
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:39,740
My Lord,

705
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:41,890
Prince Jun is afraid to bother the Lord

706
00:41:41,890 --> 00:41:43,100
and came by with the child.

707
00:41:43,100 --> 00:41:44,830
He is waiting outside the hall.

708
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:47,010
Let him in.

709
00:41:47,480 --> 00:41:50,600
Prince Jun is invited.

710
00:41:58,080 --> 00:42:00,610
My Lord, I congratulate you on your birthday.

711
00:42:01,200 --> 00:42:02,440
My wife's honored

712
00:42:02,610 --> 00:42:04,680
to have given birth to the eldest grandson of Xinchuan.

713
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:06,640
May the Lord live long and prosper.

714
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,970
Wish peace and security for Xinchuan.

715
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,340
What a blessing!

716
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:14,080
